/black-bean-burger-bowls-4-1156x1536.jpg 1156w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-4-1541x2048.jpg 1541w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-4-150x199.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-4-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOnce the burgers are cooked, I throw some more cheese on top. Since I have cheese IN the burger and ON the burger, I don’t add cheese to the salad bowl.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI realize this is shocking since cheese is my entire personality. So add it if you wish! I find that it doesn’t really need more. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"black bean burger bowls\" width=\"1737\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Black Bean Burger Bowls.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-scaled.jpg 1737w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-728x922.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-768x972.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-1213x1536.jpg 1213w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-1617x2048.jpg 1617w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-150x190.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1737px) 100vw, 1737px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201737%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-scaled.jpg 1737w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-728x922.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-768x972.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-1213x1536.jpg 1213w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-1617x2048.jpg 1617w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-150x190.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOf course, any of your other favorite burger toppings can find their way into this bowl. Or condiments. I like a drizzle of mustard. I like mustard just as much as I like pickles – in fact, I’d like to drizzle about three kinds of mustard on this bowl!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYou can always use ketchup. Even BBQ sauce or honey mustard. Or a good burger sauce, like my \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2019/07/pretzel-crusted-chicken-fingers/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehowsweeteats house sauce\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e. Sometimes I’ll use that as an extra drizzle of dressing and it’s really good.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"black bean burger bowls\" width=\"1670\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Black Bean Burger Bowls.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-scaled.jpg 1670w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-728x959.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-768x1012.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-1166x1536.jpg 1166w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-1554x2048.jpg 1554w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-150x198.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1670px) 100vw, 1670px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201670%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-scaled.jpg 1670w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-728x959.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-768x1012.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-1166x1536.jpg 1166w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-1554x2048.jpg 1554w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-150x198.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBut speaking of the dressing! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePickles are my love language. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYes, I live for pickles. I’ve loved them since I first started eating!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis pickle vinaigrette is one of my go-tos and has been for YEARS. It’s so tangy and pickle-y and briney and is perfect if you’re a huge pickle lover like I am. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"black bean burger bowls\" width=\"1755\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Black Bean Burger Bowls.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-scaled.jpg 1755w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-728x912.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-768x962.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-1226x1536.jpg 1226w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-1634x2048.jpg 1634w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-150x188.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1755px) 100vw, 1755px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201755%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-scaled.jpg 1755w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-728x912.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-768x962.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-1226x1536.jpg 1226w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-1634x2048.jpg 1634w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-150x188.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-8-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNot only do I love the flavors in this bowl, but I adore the texture. There is so much crisp, refreshing texture, crunchy bites too, and paired with the zippy dressing?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDreamy! \u003cspan id=\"more-98019\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"black bean burger bowls\" width=\"1739\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Black Bean Burger Bowls.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-10-scaled.jpg 1739w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-10-728x921.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-10-768x971.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-10-1214x1536.jpg 1214w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-10-1619x2048.jpg 1619w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-10-150x190.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1739px) 100vw, 1739px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201739%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/black-bean-burger-bowls-10-scaled.jpg 17